posting_body: ['Amazing specials - Call for details.', 'Aliso Apartments', '950 East 3rd Street, Los Angeles, CA, 90013', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 64', 'OR Text', '64', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Visit This Website to See More:', '<URL>', 'A new meaning to artistic living in DTLA', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 780 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Aliso Apartments in downtown LA is the perfect microcosm of the city, encapsulating all the characteristics and qualities you love about Los Angeles and the Arts District.', 'Here, the incredibly dynamic lifestyle spaces include studio, 1, and 2 bedroom apartments and lofts that offer an innovative concept in luxury living.', "Amid a tempting array of vintage shops, galleries à la Hauser & Wirth, and ice cream that doesn't need an Instagram filter, you’ll find your dream home, at Aliso’s DTLA apartments.", 'Garnering both name and stature from the 400-year-old Sycamore that once graced the area, Aliso Apartments provides grand-scale luxury rooted in the edgy, expressive scene affectionately known as DTLA.', 'Creative souls will feel right at home in this unique space that not only inspires expression and creativity but also fosters the drive for exploration and truly dynamic living.', 'Get in touch with us today to schedule a private tour of our new apartments in Los Angeles and see what downtown living has to offer.', 'Call Now!', 'Pet Policy', '$250 deposit for both cats and dogs.', 'For puppies & kittens under 1 year old, an additional $250 deposit applies.', 'Pet rent: $50 monthly for dogs and $35 monthly for cats.', '(All fees, deposits and charges noted above are per pet.)', 'Contact for more details.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Saturday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Sunday:12:00PM-6:00PM', 'qSk6YxrhT']
